		%h6.subheader.name
			Joel Nierman<br>VP, media and digital strategy, Liquidus

		%h6.subheader Details
		%p.caption Real-time decision engine for marketing investments.
		%ul
			%li Envision next generation user experience and suite user interface design
			%li Leapfrog competitors in the advertising analytics space
			%li Design, engineer, and launch production software

		%h6.subheader Project Type
		%p.caption UI Design, Engineering

		%h6.subheader Process
		%p.caption Learning, Envision, Blueprint, Craft, Build, Support

		%h6.subheader Price
		%p.caption $200k

